A mashup of Hungry Hungry Hippos and Angry Birds, JavaScript + HTML5 canvas element.

Includes a node.js websocket server component for a remote control.

instructions to run:

To simply run the game:
- launch index.html in Google Chrome
- run hhbKinect.app

To calibrate the Kinect better for the space available, see onscreen instructions to adjust near and far threshholds.

To use the remote control:
- make sure Web Sharing is on and that the index.html is being accessed through the server on the machine
- make sure costants.js includes the machine name or IP address of the machine it's on
- cd to the HHB directory and run "node socket.js" from the command line
- load up the remote control (gameHost.html) in Safari on an iOS device.
